# YouTube Clone Environment Variables
# Leave blank to run immediately in high-fidelity mock mode.

# OPTION A: Google Cloud Platform (Official YouTube Data API v3)
# To create an official API key, go to the Google Cloud Console,
# enable the "YouTube Data API v3", and generate an API key:
# https://console.cloud.google.com/
VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_youtube_api_key_here

# OPTION B: RapidAPI (YouTube v3 API by ytdlfree)
# Sign up at https://rapidapi.com/ytdlfree/api/youtube-v31 and copy your key:
VITE_YOUTUBE_API_KEY=bf5ced775cmsha4ff1a70ed84467p114087jsn6da0b6ce3f48
REACT_APP_RAPID_API_KEY=bf5ced775cmsha4ff1a70ed84467p114087jsn6da0b6ce3f48

